Remainder = coordinate % 48
If remainder < int(48 / 2)
    fixed_coordinate = coordinate - remainder
else
    fixed_coordinate = coordinate + remainder

The bounding box of an object gives us 4 coordinates.


Suppose:

(0, 0)   # # # #
         # # # #
         # # # #   (3, 4)

We fill all boxes/tiles within this region...

